Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: box of cats two
des: Box of Cats Second Edition helps your cats feel connected to other cats by playing multiple feline cats sounds. HOW TO USE: To Get Started: Say "Alexa open box of cats two". By default, the it will play different feline cat sounds every time you open the skill and say "meow". PREMIUM FEATURES: The Box of Cats Second Edition includes two premium packs (Feline One Pack and Feline Two Pack). FEEDBACK AND SUPPORT: If you love Box of Cats Second Edition please leave us a review. If you feel that Box of Cats Second Edition can be improved, please let us know at boxofcats1@hotmail.com and we'll do everything in our power to make it better. We'd love to hear from you! If you have questions, comments, or feedback, please e-mail us at boxofcats1@hotmail.com
